CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 14, 1964, pg. 2 reads: "Medical Committee - Members of the medical committee for the forthcoming Health-O-Rama are (left to right) Garrett Graham, associate executive director of Magee Hospital; Miss Irene Boccella, head lab technician at Magee Hospital; Dr. James A. Stewart; Dr. Oswald J. Nickens, president of the Gateway Medical Group; Dr. Charles Chesler, radiologist at Magee Hospital; Dr. Edward H. Hale, Health-O-Rama medical director; Dr. Jeanny A. Cooper, assistant pathologist at Mercy Hospital; Dr. Hugh B. Robins, health officer, and Dr. William A. Barrett, chairman of the Health-O-Rama Tripartite Committee. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Health-O-Rama medical committee members, from left: Garrett Graham, Irene Boccella, Dr. James A. Stewart; Dr. Oswald J. Nickens, Dr. Charles Chesler, Dr. Edward H. Hale, Dr. Jeanny A. Cooper, Dr. Hugh B. Robins, and Dr. William A. Barrett, gathered in conference room with wide wooden panels, another version
